Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.76,0:00:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku senang kau menolongku.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.28,0:00:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setidaknya dalam diriku, kau tampak keren.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.02,0:00:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yah, tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.70,0:00:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.58,0:00:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah baikan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.20,0:00:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.48,0:00:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.08,0:02:10.17,tanda,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}EPISODE 12: TERIMA KASIH SUDAH MENYUKAIKU
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.18,0:02:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakak, mau bagaimana makannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.42,0:02:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan makan di kamar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.82,0:02:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Letakkan di depan pintu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.88,0:02:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa jadi aku yang harus buat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.44,0:02:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakak yang buat, dong!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.84,0:02:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sedang diskors.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.64,0:02:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak bisa keluar kamar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.76,0:02:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Skors macam apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejak saat itu, aku tak tahu\Nbagaimana harus hadapi Amano.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.72,0:02:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah! Fokus belajar saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.58,0:02:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Permisi, jasa antar sudah tiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.96,0:02:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah suara ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.88,0:02:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat siang.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.74,0:02:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku membeli piza.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.46,0:02:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hiro! Selamat datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.22,0:03:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa tiba-tiba kemari?\NMasuklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.88,0:03:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku permisi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.94,0:03:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yah,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.00,0:03:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Umino sedang diskors, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.72,0:03:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin tahu keadaannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.76,0:03:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Segawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.98,0:03:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nagi bilang ia tak ingin bertemu siapa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.46,0:03:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Eh?! Skors macam apa itu?\N- Dia prihatin soal aku? Baik sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.52,0:03:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.96,0:03:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kudengar kau mencium Umino.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.50,0:03:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?! Kenapa kau tahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.94,0:03:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu pertanyaannya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.26,0:03:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasti Sachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.38,0:03:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yah, setelah kejadian seperti itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.08,0:03:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Satu-dua ciuman sebagai\Ntanda terima kasih wajar, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.34,0:03:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.42,0:03:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu benar, sih...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.80,0:03:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga tak tahu kenapa aku melakukannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.80,0:03:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang jelas aku merasa\Ntak ingin Nagi direbut.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.78,0:04:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begini, Erika.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.02,0:04:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu namanya...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.88,0:04:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Puncak dari cinta antara keluarga.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.72,0:04:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.30,0:04:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa benar begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.86,0:04:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Habis, coba pikir ulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mencium langsung ke bibir itu,\Nsudah seperti keluarga, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.74,0:04:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah! Ada benarnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ciuman asmara itu normalnya dari pipi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.32,0:04:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua perlahan dimulai dari situ.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.44,0:04:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perhitungan soal bagaimana\Ncara perdekat jarak itu juga penting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.00,0:04:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah... Segawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.70,0:04:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau ini cemburu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Imut sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.66,0:04:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, aku pulang dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.98,0:04:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih pizanya, rasanya enak.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.58,0:04:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku senang.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.74,0:04:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah lama tinggal dengan Umino,\Nakhirnya kalian jadi keluarga.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.54,0:04:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai jumpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:04:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.66,0:05:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keluarga, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.56,0:05:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini oleh-oleh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.10,0:05:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak bisa menemui Nagi, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai tak mau bertemu keluarga\Nsaat di skors, seberapa serius coba.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.44,0:05:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terdengar seperti Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.48,0:05:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, Erika...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.40,0:05:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa benar kau mencium Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.46,0:05:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi Ai merasa lega.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.74,0:05:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soalnya dengan ini kalian,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.86,0:05:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}akhirnya menjalin persahabatan\Nyang melampaui pertemanan biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.14,0:05:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, bagiku Nagi itu adalah sahabat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Betul.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.80,0:05:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Waktu kecil Ai juga mencium Nagi tiap hari.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.54,0:05:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sahabat itu begitu, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia terang-terangan berbohong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, aku pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.06,0:05:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya! Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.68,0:06:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.64,0:06:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kali ini siapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.98,0:06:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Terima kasih!\N- Pizanya datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau pesan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.96,0:06:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Habis, Kakak bilang dia tidak akan masak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.32,0:06:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak sangka mereka bawakan juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oke... Hari ini pesta piza!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.78,0:06:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi mereka berdua tadi\Nbenar-benar tak paham, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal Kakak dan Kak Erika\Ndengan ini sudah jadi rival sejati.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.48,0:06:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rival?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.92,0:06:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memang rival berciuman?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Manusia itu kalau kelewat benci\Nmalah berujung ciuman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.76,0:06:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh? Aku baru tahu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.84,0:06:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Buktinya, Kakak dan Kak Erika\Nsering bertengkar, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.10,0:06:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah! Iya juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.52,0:06:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa mungkin Amano benar-benar\Ntak menaruh perasaan apa pun padaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.48,0:06:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Yang ada kepitingnya enak sekali!\N- Itu pasti karena...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.46,0:06:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Setelah melihat Sachi menciummu,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:06:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku tak mau kalau kau direbut dariku,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.94,0:07:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}secara naluri."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.78,0:07:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebagai tanggungan,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sebagai budak,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.96,0:07:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sebagai pengurus rumah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.92,0:07:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang kaya memang menakutkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.96,0:07:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah dipermainkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.50,0:07:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Amano bersikap seperti biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.86,0:07:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sendiri yang kepikiran\Nseperti orang bodoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begini, aku harus fokus belajar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski begitu,\Nmasih sulit untukku menemuinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tahan sampai masa skorsku selesai...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.94,0:07:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, tidak ada orang...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.55,0:07:36.01,tanda,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}RAMEN ASIN
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.02,0:07:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku buat ramen saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.76,0:07:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka berdua,\Nsudah kubilang untuk buang sampah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.30,0:07:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dasar...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.76,0:07:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.68,0:07:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan begitu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.64,0:07:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin Ayah membatalkan soal itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:07:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Amano, kau di situ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soal itu? Batalkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.80,0:08:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia bicara dengan ayahnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.74,0:08:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.18,0:08:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin kau dengarkan aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.32,0:08:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku awalnya tidak sadar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.78,0:08:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku tersadar setelah bicara\Ndengan semuanya hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.12,0:08:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, maksudku...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.86,0:08:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.68,0:08:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sepertinya jatuh cinta pada Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.30,0:08:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa-apaan barusan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.98,0:08:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa maksudnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.44,0:09:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gawat! Ramennya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.76,0:09:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan-jangan kau dengar yang tadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.22,0:09:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah... Soal apa?\NAku lapar, jadi aku masak ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.96,0:09:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Telepon dari ayahmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.66,0:09:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Obrolan kalian terdengar panas, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.42,0:09:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anggap saja kau tidak dengar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soalnya pasti akan merepotkan nanti.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.16,0:09:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.44,0:09:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak! Bagaimana aku\Nbisa melakukannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.38,0:10:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini benar-benar yang namanya\Npetir di siang bolong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.08,0:10:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar, bukan? Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.02,0:10:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa memancing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.70,0:10:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sedang diskors, tahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.82,0:10:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Justru itu alasannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.06,0:10:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kupikir hidupmu sebagai\Nsiswa teladan membuatmu depresi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.92,0:10:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan terlalu dipikir,\Naku saja dulu langganan diskors.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.26,0:10:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekitar sepuluh kali.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.46,0:10:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku kasihan pada pihak sekolahmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.60,0:10:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yah... Aku tak bisa komentar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.66,0:10:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak ada salahnya kau melindungi Erika.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.34,0:10:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bangga anakku\Nbisa marah di keadaan seperti itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh? Kau bilang apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.78,0:10:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kalau dipikir...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.28,0:10:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak salah lagi\Nkalau itu yang disebut "cinta"!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa memang benar begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat pertama kali bertemu,\Nmemang aku menganggapnya cantik.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.24,0:11:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Waktuku bersamanya terasa seru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.78,0:11:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apalagi, tak mungkin begini bila\Ndicium orang yang tak kupedulikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.52,0:11:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di dunia ini ada hal yang percuma\Nkalau hanya dipikirkan terlalu lama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.10,0:11:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ajaran Keluarga Umino...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.62,0:11:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Melompatlah sebelum melihat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.54,0:11:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu benar, aku harus melompat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.32,0:11:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang juga!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.38,0:11:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Amano!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.88,0:11:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, selamat pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.90,0:11:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih sudah menyukaiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.48,0:11:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga memiliki\Nperasaan yang sama denganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.30,0:12:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang tiba-tiba kau lakukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.36,0:12:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hentikan yang seperti itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.18,0:12:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.18,0:12:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal aku sudah bersikap dewasa,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.34,0:12:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}menyuruhmu pura-pura tak dengar\Nkarena akan jadi merepotkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau malah beri aku jawaban?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.94,0:12:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kubilang, aku juga rasakan hal yang sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.68,0:12:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, tidak, tidak!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.60,0:12:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku senang mendengarnya,\Ntapi aku belum sesiap itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.86,0:12:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.90,0:12:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang ini pertandingan baru saja mulai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.22,0:12:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan tiba-tiba mau buat gol!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.80,0:12:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah kubilang, kita itu sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.14,0:12:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga mungkin sudah jatuh cinta padamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.22,0:12:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.34,0:12:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena itu, ayo kita pergi
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.34,0:12:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ke tempat ayahmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.54,0:12:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa cuma Erika yang tak bisa\Nke kebun binatang dengan Ayah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.58,0:13:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Teman-teman SD-ku bilang mereka\Npernah pergi bersama ayah mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.30,0:13:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi Erika tidak pernah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nyonya Muda...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayah Anda adalah orang yang sangat sibuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebagai putri direktur,\NAnda tidak boleh bersikap manja.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.96,0:13:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi Erika ingin pergi ke kebun binatang!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, mari pergi dengan saya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.66,0:13:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita akan ambil banyak foto\Nuntuk Ayah Anda lihat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.22,0:13:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nyonya Muda?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.98,0:13:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayah Anda adalah orang yang hebat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.44,0:13:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beliau juga tampil di TV, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.76,0:13:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayah Anda juga dikenal di negara saya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.02,0:13:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Papa selalu dikelilingi\Norang-orang penting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.02,0:13:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak bisa mendekatinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.82,0:13:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Habis, Papa adalah raja hotel yang terkenal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.42,0:13:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berhenti tinggal bersama?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.70,0:13:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:14:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebelum festival budaya,\Naku dipanggil dan diberi tahu oleh Ayah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.72,0:14:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yah... Aku juga berprasangka, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.18,0:14:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, boleh kuanggap kalau kau\Ningin temui Ayah karena kau tak mau?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.80,0:14:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yah, ada benarnya juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.78,0:14:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga tak mau kebebasanku diambil.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.82,0:14:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.46,0:14:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat kusampaikan itu lewat telepon,\Nteleponku keburu ditutup oleh Ayah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.14,0:14:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku lega karena Nagi bersamaku sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.22,0:14:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lega?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.80,0:14:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau aku sendiri,\Naku tak bisa sampaikan dengan lancar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.54,0:14:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu kalau hubungan mereka renggang.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak kusangka separah ini,\Nmeskipun mereka ayah dan anak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.70,0:14:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf membuat kalian ke tempat seperti ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.20,0:14:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena urusannya mendadak,\Naku tak bisa batalkan pekerjaan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pekerjaan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku punya ide membangun\Nhotel terapung di laut.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.80,0:15:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari ini aku datang untuk survei.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.24,0:15:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa Anda dengar dari Amano?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.52,0:15:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami masih tak ingin\Nberhenti tinggal bersama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.80,0:15:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.90,0:15:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah bilang, kan? Papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau aku... dengan Nagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.44,0:15:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana denganmu, Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.66,0:15:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana perasaanmu terhadap Erika?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.78,0:15:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.48,0:15:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.74,0:15:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga menyimpan rasa cinta padanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.22,0:15:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan bilang terus terang begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.88,0:15:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baru pertama kali kulihat Papa tertawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.44,0:15:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ada yang lucu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.06,0:15:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya lengah sedikit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.80,0:15:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh-duh,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.10,0:15:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}apa itu jawaban kalian,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.32,0:15:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}setelah setengah tahun tinggal bersama\Nsebagai pasangan muda?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.86,0:15:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Eh?\N- Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.58,0:15:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena hampir tak terjadi apa-apa,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.02,0:15:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kupikir pernikahan\Nakan mustahil bagi kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.70,0:16:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu alasanku ingin kalian\Nberhenti tinggal bersama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.78,0:16:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi ternyata kalian masih sebatas\Nsadar akan perasaan masing-masing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.34,0:16:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang tuaku pun begitu,\Nada sesuatu yang aneh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa pasangan di dunia ini\Nmelangkah lebih cepat dari kami?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.02,0:16:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan habiskan waktu sebagai pelajar\Nyang berharga dengan sia-sia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.38,0:16:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian sadar akan perasan masing-masing\Nsetelah setengah tahun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana kalau gunakan momen ini\Nuntuk jaga jarak sementara?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.58,0:16:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.64,0:16:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana, kata Anda?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.56,0:16:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang ini bukannya ingin kami menikah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.10,0:16:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anu...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Papa dan Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.74,0:16:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Papa dan Mama butuh 10 tahun untuk menikah
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.80,0:16:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}setelah festival budaya itu, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.58,0:16:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.34,0:16:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami baru menikah\Nsetelah kuliah dan bekerja.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.02,0:17:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di selang waktu itu,\Napa yang terjadi di antara kalian?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm... Kau benar juga...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.20,0:17:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau tak salah, kami baru pegangan tangan\Nsetelah pacaran tiga tahun
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.54,0:17:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan berciuman setelah empat tahun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.64,0:17:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tidak berkomentar soal kami, dong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.04,0:17:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.98,0:17:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, aku juga ingin begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.20,0:17:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga ingin menjalani cinta\Nyang perlahan seperti itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.94,0:17:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.68,0:17:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi begitu hubungan asmara\Nyang Amano inginkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.32,0:17:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak sangka akan tiba hari\Ndi mana Erika bilang begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.74,0:17:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Layaknya diriku dulu,\Nmungkin memang beginilah pasangan SMA.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.36,0:17:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari ini aku jadi teringat\Nmasa laluku setelah bertemu kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.88,0:17:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tampaknya aku terlalu tergesa-gesa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.54,0:17:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soal kelanjutan kalian,\Nkuputuskan memantau dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.82,0:18:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku senang kau bersamaku hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.68,0:18:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.62,0:18:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena kau berani mulai pembicaraan,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.14,0:18:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku akhirnya bisa sampaikan\Nyang kupikirkan pada Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.42,0:18:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yah... Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau harus lebih sering hadapi dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya! Akan kulakukan itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.90,0:18:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Demi mengarungi panjangnya hidup,\Nbutuh yang namanya persiapan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.74,0:18:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bodoh namanya jika bertualang\Nhanya bermodal nekat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.60,0:18:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memiliki kehati-hatian\Nadalah sikap yang tepat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.48,0:18:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tetapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.92,0:18:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, Nagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.80,0:18:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita mulai lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.44,0:18:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.28,0:18:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.16,0:18:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mohon bantuannya dari sekarang!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.22,0:18:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu pula aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.12,0:18:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ceritanya tidak akan berjalan\Nsesuai tempo yang kalian tetapkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.52,0:19:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya tak akan berjalan\Nsesuai rencanamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.58,0:19:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perutku lapar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.94,0:19:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Kakak. Kami lapar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.44,0:19:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.62,0:19:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Proses belajarku terhambat\Ngara-gara diskors, tahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.12,0:19:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masak saja sendiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.68,0:19:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh? Mau pesan piza?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.14,0:19:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah bosan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.04,0:19:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat malam!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.00,0:19:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hiro dan Ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.72,0:19:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin mereka bawakan kita piza?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.10,0:19:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami permisi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.34,0:19:40.83,tanda,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}KUIL MEGURO MYOUJIN\NPANDUAN UPACARA PERNIKAHAN
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.84,0:19:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampel brosurnya sudah jadi, lo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.90,0:19:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serius?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.50,0:19:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Walau bukan piza, aku senang!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.14,0:19:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin lihat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.46,0:19:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Foto semuanya ada, lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.70,0:19:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah kunantikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak terlalu tertarik.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.58,0:19:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah! Sachi juga ada, lo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:19:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.10,0:20:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berbau kriminal, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami juga ingin memasukkan\Nunsur seragam kali ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.88,0:20:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi yang terbaik memang aku\Nyang pakai pakaian Jepang!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.16,0:20:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cocok sekali untuk pernikahan\Ndi Meguro Myojin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.36,0:20:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Si tak mau kalah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.84,0:20:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pakaian Tiongkok juga cocok!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.08,0:20:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.02,0:20:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mulai sekarang harus dipromosikannya\Nke seluruh dunia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.76,0:20:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau tidak,\Ntakkan bisa bertahan secara global.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.16,0:20:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah! Fotonya benar-benar bagus!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.00,0:20:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa suatu saat hari seperti ini\Njuga akan datang dalam hidupku?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.78,0:20:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gaun juga cocok, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.60,0:20:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuilku memang hebat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.08,0:20:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu yang kau puji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.64,0:20:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dasar, Hiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.72,0:20:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini bagus juga!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.04,0:20:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ini sebenarnya
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.30,0:20:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Iya!\N- Imut sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.34,0:20:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}akan berakhir dengan siapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.58,0:21:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi ini sudah agak kasihan, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.88,0:21:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.82,0:21:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti kriminal, ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.84,0:21:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cocok dengan Kakak, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.94,0:21:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh? Apa maksud kalian?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.76,0:21:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.04,0:21:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibuku tetap bersikeras, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.18,0:21:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.58,0:21:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.56,0:21:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kemunculan Si Inisial U yang kedua kali.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.18,0:21:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibuku tampaknya\Nketagihan menonton berita itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.68,0:21:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak benci ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.34,0:21:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa-apaan ini?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.32,0:21:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Foto ini sungguh bagus!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.12,0:21:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau benar!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.26,0:21:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini karena modelnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.62,0:21:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh kupakai ini di situsku?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.50,0:21:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nagi, aku lapar.\NBuatkan sesuatu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.76,0:21:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga! Aku belum makan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.06,0:21:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga ingin turut dijamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.34,0:21:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakak! Buatkan katsudon empat porsi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.92,0:22:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Umino. Nagi.\N- Kakak.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.80,0:22:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana sebenarnya masa depanku nanti?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.30,0:23:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana kalau
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.22,0:23:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kita berpacaran?
